Package: owidR
Type: Package
Title: A package for getting data from Our World in Data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Piers York
Maintainer: Piers York <piersyork+owidr@gmail.com>
Description: Scrapes data from the Our World in Data website to offer easy to use functions for searching for datasets and downloading them into R.
Imports: dplyr, rvest, readr, leaflet, stringr, ggplot2, sf, magrittr, htmltools, forcats, jsonlite, knitr, rstudioapi, purrr, xml2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
